{"tid":2005890,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)蛇叔大逃亡1-2 殺人硬件6.7 活火溶城","createTime":"2020-05-07T11:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T19:30:02.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3d2b3c768007ebbbcc79c7a5f5e3a67bc85043","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=7af6aba1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=ecc9e638\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=81f2fda5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4b/EscapefromNYposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4b%2FEscapefromNYposter.jpg&h=fd0d0b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/71/Escape_From_LA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F71%2FEscape_From_LA.jpg&h=421ef439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/b/bf/Virtuosity_poster.jpg/220px-Virtuosity_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fbf%2FVirtuosity_poster.jpg%2F220px-Virtuosity_poster.jpg&h=110093d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/dd/Volcano_%281997_film%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fd%2Fdd%2FVolcano_%25281997_film%2529.jpg&h=58ab5b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.電影設定於1997年的近未來美國，當時紐約市的曼哈頓島已經成為廢墟，並也是一座重刑犯監獄。當美國總統所搭乘的空軍一號被劫持並墜落在紐約後，他成為了人質，使得特種部隊隊長（李&middot;范&middot;克里夫 飾）與退伍軍人兼重刑犯大蛇&middot;普利斯金（寇特&middot;羅素 飾）達成交易，被賦予在二十四小時內將總統救出的危險任務..<br />\n<br />\n2.2000年8月23日，一場地震襲擊了洛杉磯，造成聖費爾南多谷的洪水和加州部分分裂為馬里布和阿納海姆。片中敘述，繼上次的紐約事件的十幾年後，大蛇&middot;普利斯金再度被2013年的新總統放出並加以威脅，要求在十小時內前往已被恐怖份子柯佛&middot;瓊斯占據的洛杉磯將電磁脈衝武器「黑盒子」奪回，因此這次遭威脅的大蛇逼不得已，只好潛入危險重重的洛杉磯..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.此期時正值是一個電腦侵佔人類的世界，一切都以電腦程式為先。而電腦人魔Sid 6.7（羅素高爾飾）就在這段時間誕生，他是集一百八十三個連環殺手的精華合製而成的，且四出謀殺了許多無辜者。為緝拿此電腦殺手，警方派前兇殺組督察柏加賓斯（丹素華盛頓飾）全力緝魔，以免釀成更多的悲劇；而賓斯對狂魔恨之切骨，皆因其妻子及女兒均死於他的手上...<br />\n<br />\n4..電影中的背景位於洛杉磯，在一次疑是煤氣管爆炸意外中，七名維修下水道的工人被活活燒死在事發現場。洛杉磯危機處理中心主任馬克迅速趕往事發地點進行深入調查，由於連日的地震災害，政府遂派出地質學家艾美與馬克聯手合作；馬克與地質學家發現該處的地質出現了不尋常的活動，又發現由於板塊移動造成地層斷裂，而在裂縫中正不斷溢出一種溫度極高的液體，隨時引發火山爆發<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=9f27e6ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=291e9c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89d5b0c34379a65f968cb03f6f8803dc11c17de","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T11:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894148a8659e7db2759be006c234e591a19eaf40","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54fd6a4cbb189fb98164a8a7f82bdc3ed42e3e1","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb7e4b2979d1771e0e3c9fbd9a6eaf656fe248","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T18:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277f44ff9610d306a9d74c275cd1d1edb456e35d","tid":2005890,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass